form for scientific computation. We also present the results of\nexperiments done with various configuration parameters of the proposed\narchitecture, to show its utility in adapting to a range of scientific\napplications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2015 17:27:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-20"}
