 L1 index imbalance can thus result in\nloss of concurrency and reduced aggregate throughput.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2015 21:13:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2015 20:05:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-01"}
